            </label>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details open class="border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-5 py-4 font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">5 · Numerator phenotypes</summary>
          <div class="px-5 pb-5 space-y-3">
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">What you are counting in the numerator. Pick from each library as relevant; drug exposures for utilisation metrics, outcomes for incidence / prevalence, mortality causes for cause-specific mortality. Free-text fields below for codes not in the libraries.</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
              <button type="button" data-open-library data-category="exposures" data-target-name="exposureName" data-target-codes="exposureCodes" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-brand-700 bg-brand-50 hover:bg-brand-100 border border-brand-200 px-2 py-1 rounded transition">📚 Pick exposure</button>
              <button type="button" data-open-library data-category="outcomes" data-target-name="outcomeName" data-target-codes="outcomeCodes" data-target-def="outcomeDef" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-brand-700 bg-brand-50 hover:bg-brand-100 border border-brand-200 px-2 py-1 rounded transition">📚 Pick outcome</button>
