            </label>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details open class="border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer select-none px-5 py-4 font-semibold text-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">8 · Age-standardisation
            <span class="ml-2 text-[10px] font-normal text-slate-500 normal-case tracking-normal">(active when "Age-standardised rates" is ticked above)</span>
